Title: Operon BPM-Trendy 16 Wrist Bp Monitor
Description: With the Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor you could now measure your blood pressure at the privacy of your own home and be able to obtain the same level of accuracy that hospital professionals depend on.  Using a simple yet advanced operating technology, this blood pressure detector allows Easy Self-Testing. The home monitoring facility of this blood pressure monitor helps you keep a constant check on your blood pressure level and alerts you and your doctors to possible health complications. In addition to this, the device also offers Irregular Heart Beat Detection, notifying you of your health condition and helping you prevent serious health problems. Build This modern blood pressure monitor from Operon comes with a huge LCD display, giving you a better view of your heart beat and blood pressure readings.  Furthermore, this clear digital display shows the date and time of your readings. The trendily designed blood pressure monitor has a flexible wrist cuff and its circumference ranges from 12.5 x 21 cm. This compact Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor comprising of WHO indicator weighs 120g making it an easily portable device and has dimensions of 67.7mm x 87.4 mm x 32.3 mm (WXHXD).  Monitoring your blood pressure with this wrist type blood pressure monitor involves a quick three step process. All you need to do is simply wrap the cuff around our wrist and make sure the cuff is placed in the right manner.  You could then turn on the start button on the control panel. The cuff will automatically inflate at the touch of the start button, reading your heart rate and checking your blood pressure. Performance The Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist Bp Monitor has an in-built inflation detection function which allows instant inflation of the cuff to an optimal level, providing you quick and precise readings. The blood pressure readings of this wrist type monitor are equal to Auscultation- cuff/stethescope method and hence capable of giving you accurate and consistent measurements. Enabling a 2 user facility, this digitalized blood pressure monitor is bestowed with a 90 readings memory and capable of providing an average measurement of the last 3 readings. This helps you keep  a continuous track on the progression in your blood and heart rate levels. Apart from this Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor is also embedded with a 3 Set Alarm Setting, thereby providing remarkable operating performance. Adding to the comfort, this smart blood pressure monitor has a Low Battery Indicator which saves power and increases battery life. This digital Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor displays readings ranging from 30 to 280 mmHg for pressure readings and 40 to 199 beats/minute for pulse rates. The accuracy rate of the BP monitor is regulated at +/-3 mmHg for pressure reading and +/-4% of reading for pulse progress.  This trendy device is powered by 2 x 1.5V AAA Alkaline batteries.

Title: Niscomed CMS-50D Pulse Oximeter(White, Blue)
Description: Niscomed CMS-50 Pulse Oximeter The Niscomed CMS-50 pulse oximeter has been immaculately engineered to effectively determine and read your pulse rate and oxygen percentage in your blood in the comforts of your own home. This Niscomed CMS-50 is a fingertip oximeter that needs to be clipped onto your fingers and preferably your index finger for the light sensors in the oximeter to quickly and precisely sense and measure the saturated oxygen in your blood.BuildBuilt to enhance comfort and ease of use, this Niscomed pulse oximeter is user-friendly and simple in its operation, capable of delivering fast and easy spot-checks. This pulse oximeter is small and compact, thereby allowing enhanced portability. Armed with a clear and easy-to-view LED screen, this Niscomed pulse oximeter capably displays your pulse rates and blood saturated oxygen levels in BPM and SpO2 units respectively shown along a pleth waveform.The LED display in the Niscomed CMS-50 pulse oximeter functions with enhanced efficacy as it is equipped with dual display colors and four-levels adjustable brightness features, making it convenient for you. You can also view your readings comfortably as this pulse oximeter allows six modes of display directions enabling you to read your results in six different angles.PerformanceThe Niscomed pulse oximter provides a safe and comfortable measuring procedure as this device utilizes a non-invasive method to procure your saturated oxygen readings or the amount of oxygen carried by the hemoglobin in your red blood cells. You simply have to place your fingers between the clip-ons in the device and press the button for your measurement process to function.This pulse oximeter utilizes light-emitting diodes to detect the oxygen content in your blood. When you start the device, it emits light which immediately passes through the sensors in your skin, measuring the hemoglobin in your blood. Two types of lights comprising of red and infrared are emitted, wherein the oxygenated blood absorbs the wavelength of the red light and the deoxygenated blood absorbs the wavelength of the infrared light.While the oxygenated and deoxygenated blood absorb different light wavelengths, the oximeter operates to find the ratio between the two and gives you the relative measurement, therefore providing you an accurate estimate of your blood oxygen saturation.Besides performing efficiently and delivering accurate results, the Niscomed pulse oximeter also comes with convenient features that give you a comfortable user experience. The Auto shut-off feature in the Niscomed CMS-50 pulse oximeter enables the device to immediately shut down if left idle for more than 5 seconds, therefore conserving energy and allowing safe usage. Moreover, the display format is also saved when your device shuts down automatically, preventing data loss.For enhanced convenience, this Pulse oximeter also displays your battery status and indicates when your battery is low. This Niscomed pulse oximeter requires 2 AAA batteries to function soundly.
CategoryName: Electronics>Health and Personal Care>Health Care>Pulse Oximeters

Title: Healthbuddy Zerotox Herbal Pre Shave Oil, 210ml & Handmade After Shave Lotion, 210ml
Description: Apart from softening your skin Healthbuddy Zerotox Herbal After Shave Lotion refreshes your skin avoiding the stingy razor burns. It smoothens, firms and polishes your texture every day. This is a light & mild lotion that is made with all-natural ingredients like Purified Water, Beeswax, Vitamin-E, Peppermint Oil, Aloevera Extract, Neem Extract and Camphor. It is also free from alcohol which prevents irritation, dryness and itchiness on your skin after application. It is antibacterial – so it eliminates bacteria and virus present on skin to avoid suffering from clogged pores and acne. Being manufactured under the Zerotox banner signifies it to be a toxic-free product that it is SLS and Paraben free. To properly apply Healthbuddy Zerotox Handmade After Shave Lotion, squeeze a small amount of the lotion on to the palms of your hand. Rub your hands together and apply the lotion evenly across the shaved area including the neck. Apply a dime-sized amount and ride off to take on the world!Shaving is an integral part of men’s regular grooming rituals and calls for detailed attention and care. It makes your skin dry, rough and exposes your skin to many dermal problems like itching, irritation, razor bumps, burns, inflammations and even ingrown hair issues over time. Healthbuddy Zerotox brings you an easy pre-shave conditioning system that hydrates your whiskers for a comfortable and smooth close shave with minimal or no irritation. Healthbuddy Zerotox Handmade Pre Shave Oil is a lightweight and natural lubricating oil fortified with the goodness of Almond, Jojoba, Eucalyptus and Rosemary. Over and above that being a presentation by the Zerotox brand, the oil comes free of any added toxins like SLS and Paraben. It contains no alcohol or mineral oil and is vegan without any animal component. Furthermore, the oil has skin-smoothening properties and balances skin oil production too. On application it makes your skin super-soft and works as a natural antiseptic with great medicinal and healing effects. Its mild aroma does not get heady and synchronizes well with your favourite shaving cream, soap, aftershave or cologne. The oil renders a protective lubrication layer between your delicate facial skin and the sharp edge of the razor, therefore reducing the skin irritation that often occurs as a result of shaving. By softening the stubble, it allows the razor to move smoothly. To properly apply this pre shave oil, rinse your face thoroughly with warm water and apply a few drops of oil to the palm of your hand. Rub your palms together and gently massage the oil onto your face across the entire shaving area with equal coverage of the oil. Let the oil set on your skin for at least a minute. Apply your soap or cream lather to your face and proceed to shave as normal.

Title: Devinez 15-2009, Cinnamon Essential Oil, 100% Pure, Natural & Undiluted(15 ml)
Description: Cinnamon is one of the most popular herbs for flavoring and medicinal uses. Although cinnamon oil has numerous health benefits, it often causes irritations and allergic reactions. Therefore people prefer to use cinnamon directly instead of using the oil. The herb, owing to its vast medicinal uses, has found a prominent position in traditional medicines, especially in Ayurveda, which is the traditional Indian medicinal system. Traditionally, cinnamon has been used in many cultures for treating a variety of health disorders including diarrhea, arthritis, menstrual cramps, heavy menstruation, yeast infections, colds, flu, and digestive problems. Cinnamon is now being used all over the world for the treatment of a variety of health disorders including respiratory problems, skin infections, blood impurity, menstrual problems, and various heart disorders. The most important part of cinnamon is its bark, which can be used in a variety of ways.

Description: Jasmine sambac oil is extracted from the white flowers of the jasmine sambac plant that usually blossom at night. You can also use jasmine sambac oil as a perfume to attain a refreshed feel throughout the day.

Title: Devinez 15-2034, Spikenard Essential Oil, 100% Pure, Natural & Undiluted(15 ml)
Description: This plant is very famous on the Indian Subcontinent by the name of Jatamansi and is widely used in herbal medicines. Several herbal, medicinal preparations based on this plant can be found on the market, particularly in India and a few of its neighboring countries. This plant is native to Nepal and is called Nardostachys Jatamansi in botanical terminology. The health benefits of Spikenard Essential Oil can be attributed to its properties as an antibacterial, anti-fungal, anti-inflammatory, deodorant, laxative, sedative and uterine substance. The traditional use of this plant was for the skin. Due to its earthy and somewhat wet, soil-like smell, which resembles the smell of moss, it is also used in aromatherapy as a sedative and calming agent.The essential oil of Spikenard is extracted by steam distillation of the resin obtained from this plant and it contains aristolene, calarene, clalarenol, coumarin, dihydroazulenes, jatamanshinic acid, nardol, nardostachone, valerianol, valeranal and valeranone as its chief components, which are the sources of its medicinal properties.

Title: Devinez 15-2020, Lemon Essential Oil, 100% Pure, Natural & Undiluted(15 ml)
Description: Lemon Oil is derived from the Lemon tree, which is a small thorny evergreen tree native to India. Having good therapeutic and aromatherapy properties, it assists in providing the utmost level of relief to the brain for alleviating the conditions of headaches & migraines. When used for skin massage, Lemon oil also assists in clearing various skin related problems related to acne, greasy skin, and easing painful cold sores. It also helps in relieving mouth ulcers, herpes and insect bites. The health benefits of lemon oil can be attributed to its stimulating, calming, carminative, anti-infection, astringent, detoxifying, antiseptic, disinfectant, sleep inducing, and antifungal properties. The benefits of lemon oil include its ability to treat stress disorders, fever, infections, asthma, obesity, insomnia, skin disorders, hair conditions, stomach problems and tiredness.

Description: Palmarosa Essential Oil is also known by the name of Cymbopogon martinii and is a species of grass from lemon grass genus. The oil is also well recognized as a effective insect repellent. The oil is used in soaps and perfumes. Further, it is also applied to stored grain & beans as it is antihelmintic against nematodes and has antifungal and mosquito repellent properties. It is extensively used in culinary applications. It tastes hot and has an appetizing aroma. Black pepper is the dried fruit of the pepper plant, whose scientific name is Piper Nigrum.The main components of its essential oil are Limonene, Pinene, Myrcene, Phellandrene, Beta Caryophyllene, Beta Bisabolene, Sabinene, Linalol, Pinocarveol, Alpha Termineol, Camphene and Alpha Terpenene. Each box of 100% Botanical hair colour contains 2 packets for one to two application, depending on your hair length . Boil 3 cups of pure water. Pour one/cup of boiled water into the powder, stirring continuously with a non metallic spoon or spatula to break the lumps. Add enough of the boiled water to obtain a honey like consistency of the paste. After that keep the mixture for 1-2 minutes for thicken and stabilize. Apply mixture at the crown of the head, coating all strands with the help of supplied brush or Fingers. Leave mixture on your head for 30-45 minutes. Title: AirFIne 30 Second Style Hair Extension
Description: Add length, fullness color and highlights to your hair easily with a ponytail hairpiece addition. They attach in just seconds, giving you an instant new look that will leave them wondering how you did it. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions is a long length synthetic clip-on ponytail hairpiece with layered effects and out curls. It features a 2-in-1 attachment, and can be attached to your hair quickly and easily by claw clip. Features - It is a 2 in 1 readymade looks (Straight and Curls) pony tail hair extension available in 2 colors - Hot Fudge (Black) and Brownie Finesse (Dark Brown), Top grade quality synthetic hair which look close to natural hair, This product is made from the highest quality heat resistant (less than 180 degree C) synthetic fibers, 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions can be experimented with various hair accessories for new looks every day, It can easily gel up with your hair, and gives you a perfect party look each time, Product Details - Length - Long, 22 Inches, Texture - Way/Out Curls, Fiber -Synthetic, Type ? Ponytails, Colors - Natural Black and Natural Dark Brown, Weight - 110 gm. Benefits - You can increase length of your hair by 22 inches, and change your looks in just couple of seconds, It adds volume to your hair, so that you can flaunt your looks and new hairstyle, Saves time and money, Low maintenance, Ready to go hair style, can be applied in less than 30 seconds, Easy to carry and useful for all kinds of events and functions. How to Use - Make a tight high pony with the help of thin ruffle band, Now hold the clutcher opening it away from you and wear it over your pony hiding your own hair inside, Comb a bit with fingers to get the final style in seconds. Precautions and Care - Generally speaking, it should be washed once every 6-8 uses, though this number can vary depending on your own personal preferences. You should consider washing the hair extensions if the style begins to lose its luster, becomes more difficult to style, or simply doesn't feel as fresh as before. For cleaning the hair extensions - take water in a tub and add some normal shampoo. Now put the hair extensions by gently rinsing it and washing it thrice with clean water. Do not rub, wring, twist, brush or comb the hair extensions while it is wet. When the hair extensions is dry enough not to drip, turn it right side out and place the hair extensions directly on the drying stand. Never use heat on synthetic hairs in an attempt to dry them faster, When the hair extensions are dry; letting the strands fall back into place. Then, simply brush or comb the hair extensions into the desired look. Do not brush hair extensions - finger style, or use a pick comb instead. Do not simply leave the hair extensions lying around - when not in use, place the hair extensions in a pouch/box to help preserve its shape and styling. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions is innovative pony tail hair extensions which come with readymade 2 in 1 hair style. It is made up of Swiss synthetic fibres which look very close to natural hairs that gel up easily with natural human hair. The hair extensions are so silky to touch and feel that you may get confuse sometimes with your natural hair. It attaches to your existing hair quickly and easily with a claw clip. They are so simple to use and light to carry that you would like to wear them in every occasion you go. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions, the pony tail hair extensions are available in 2 colour options, i.e. Hot Fudge (Natural Black) and Brownie Finesse (Dark Brown). It is not limited to just 2 in 1 readymade hair style but can also be experimented with curler to get it desired curls ( Please make sure the temperature of curler is below 180 degree C). Warranty - 3 Years Shelf Life.

Title: AirFine 30 Second Style Hair Extension
Description: Add length, fullness color and highlights to your hair easily with a ponytail hairpiece addition. They attach in just seconds, giving you an instant new look that will leave them wondering how you did it. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions is a long length synthetic clip-on ponytail hairpiece with layered effects and out curls. It features a 2-in-1 attachment, and can be attached to your hair quickly and easily by claw clip. Features - It is a 2 in 1 readymade looks (Straight and Curls) pony tail hair extension available in 2 colors - Hot Fudge (Black) and Brownie Finesse (Dark Brown), Top grade quality synthetic hair which look close to natural hair, This product is made from the highest quality heat resistant (less than 180 degree C) synthetic fibers, 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions can be experimented with various hair accessories for new looks every day, It can easily gel up with your hair, and gives you a perfect party look each time, Product Details - Length - Long, 22 Inches, Texture - Way/Out Curls, Fiber -Synthetic, Type ? Ponytails, Colors - Natural Black and Natural Dark Brown, Weight - 110 gm. Benefits - You can increase length of your hair by 22 inches, and change your looks in just couple of seconds, It adds volume to your hair, so that you can flaunt your looks and new hairstyle, Saves time and money, Low maintenance, Ready to go hair style, can be applied in less than 30 seconds, Easy to carry and useful for all kinds of events and functions. How to Use - Make a tight high pony with the help of thin ruffle band, Now hold the clutcher opening it away from you and wear it over your pony hiding your own hair inside, Comb a bit with fingers to get the final style in seconds. Precautions and Care - Generally speaking, it should be washed once every 6-8 uses, though this number can vary depending on your own personal preferences. You should consider washing the hair extensions if the style begins to lose its luster, becomes more difficult to style, or simply doesn't feel as fresh as before. For cleaning the hair extensions - take water in a tub and add some normal shampoo. Now put the hair extensions by gently rinsing it and washing it thrice with clean water. Do not rub, wring, twist, brush or comb the hair extensions while it is wet. When the hair extensions is dry enough not to drip, turn it right side out and place the hair extensions directly on the drying stand. Never use heat on synthetic hairs in an attempt to dry them faster, When the hair extensions are dry; letting the strands fall back into place. Then, simply brush or comb the hair extensions into the desired look. Do not brush hair extensions - finger style, or use a pick comb instead. Do not simply leave the hair extensions lying around - when not in use, place the hair extensions in a pouch/box to help preserve its shape and styling. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions is innovative pony tail hair extensions which come with readymade 2 in 1 hair style. It is made up of Swiss synthetic fibres which look very close to natural hairs that gel up easily with natural human hair. The hair extensions are so silky to touch and feel that you may get confuse sometimes with your natural hair. It attaches to your existing hair quickly and easily with a claw clip. They are so simple to use and light to carry that you would like to wear them in every occasion you go. 30 Seconds Style Curly Hair Extensions, the pony tail hair extensions are available in 2 colour options, i.e. Hot Fudge (Natural Black) and Brownie Finesse (Dark Brown). It is not limited to just 2 in 1 readymade hair style but can also be experimented with curler to get it desired curls ( Please make sure the temperature of curler is below 180 degree C). Warranty - 3 Years Shelf Life.
